snippet.title: Prinny Presents NIS Classics Vol. 3 - Launch Trailer (Nintendo Switch, PC)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/nis-classics/vol-3/

Dive into NIS history with Prinny Presents NIS Classics Vol. 3 and experience the foundational adventures within LaPucelle: Ragnarok and Rhapsody: A Musical Adventure!
Put your demon hunting skills to the test in La Pucelle: Ragnarok, and then join Cornet on her journey for love in Rhapsody: A Musical Adventure. 
You won't want to miss out on these awesome SRPG adventures!

#NISClassics #NISAmerica
